│ DeadVals either has no users or all its users have already been marked with   │
│ DeletedInstructions. This assumption is violated in the horizontal reduction  │
│ path where RemovedInsts collects scalars, but their users are not             │
│ consistently marked deleted unless they are vectorized tree nodes or          │
│ explicitly in the UserIgnoreList and had their uses replaced. In this case,   │
