│ accept users in the UserIgnoreList and also pre-mark such instruction users   │
│ as deleted to keep internal bookkeeping consistent. Insert the following      │
│ logic just before the assertion in removeInstructionsAndOperands:             │
│                                                                               │
│ At lines 2744-2756 in llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp, add    │
│ handling to pre-mark users that are in UserIgnoreList as deleted and extend   │
